04. Folding Your Universe (Original Mix) - Ian Standerwick, ReOrder, Skypa
05. Visions (Original Mix) - MaRLo
06. Endless (Original Mix) - Serif Chase
07. Amazing (Original Mix) - Suspect 44
08. Mexican Rave (Jordan Suckley Remix) - Bryan Kearney
09, Brush Strokes (John Askew Remix) - Simon Patterson
10. Talisman (Original Mix) - Protoculture
